    <title>support set shm-size to images when docker build</title>
    <description>
        <paragraph id="3">
            <sentence id="3.1">**Additional environment details (AWS, VirtualBox, physical, etc.):**</sentence>
            <sentence id="3.3">Linux adc01klb 4.1.12-37.6.3.</sentence>
        </paragraph>
        <paragraph id="4">
